@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ylxiho(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.65 / v1 + 0.85)))
    tmp = (v1 - ((v2 + 0.31 - v0 + 0.07) * (v2 + 0.03 * tmp + 0.66)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin(wp.sin(v2 + 0.02)))
    data[tid] = v0
